reviewText: It is what it is. I don't always know what's happening and why, but in the end I'm thrilled and amused. Much better than 95% of movies you see in our American movie theaters.

the good news is the usual low price for these
the bad news is they really could've been great movies

so not bad for your collection, but not great either, but hey, not every movie can be fantastic and if it entertains you, then no harm- no foul
